# Figures

The publication figures are produced from the locked summary JSONs in `../results`.

- Figure 3 (matched-capacity ablation) and Figure 5 (cross-domain dissociation) are
  drawn from the DIAT-µSAT ablation and the close-the-square run.
- Figure 4 (two SHD splits) is drawn from the mixed-split bake-off and the official
  speaker-disjoint re-run; the Spearman correlation is 0.76.

The manuscript figures were rendered with a single MATLAB / Octave script against
these numbers. Drop that script here to regenerate the PDFs, or read the values
directly from `../results/*.json`.
